ComicInfo.Title: Crossed Wires, Part 2; Urotsukidoggy; The Date; The Ups And Downs Of Anthropomorphic Relationships, Part 2
ComicInfo.Summary:
Crossed Wires, Part 2: Sally's mystery caller reveals his identity.
Urotsukidoggy: An astronaut is set upon deep in space by a tentacled mutant plant.
The Date: Skyler and Galen go out to dinner. Nikki tries to break up the date, fearing that Skyler will become more popular with the guys than she is.
The Ups And Downs Of Anthropomorphic Relationships, Part 2: Dr. Lee and her unwilling assistant once again demonstrate the problems of inter-species sex.
